narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would absolutely recommend to a fellow student; the work load is really not bad and all of the work is exciting because it's preparation to go on this super cool field trip over the summer.
Take this class if you want to learn geology skills in the field. This requires mental preparation and some level of physical competence.
yes, if they are interested in or think they would be interested in geology research. It would really be improved though with demanding a little more work from each student.
Will be worth it for the trip!
